 I wrote to Ling at one point asking him if he had considered using the Polanyi adsorption

00:23:38.980 --> 00:23:48.140
 isotherm because of this intrinsic field idea that was built into it.

00:23:48.140 --> 00:24:02.420
 And he said no, the one he was using, Langmuir, I guess it was, works fine.

