 ordering page and it took six months or so for the orders to drop off.

03:50:48.940 --> 03:50:56.640
 But I was not only running out of books, but I was taking up a big part of my time to package

03:50:56.640 --> 03:51:02.280
 and mail books.

03:51:02.280 --> 03:51:08.280
 Are you aware of people who are translating your work and also trying to help and counsel

03:51:08.280 --> 03:51:09.280
 people?

